608 template<typename ASTNodeClass>
609 class chillAST_Child {
610 private:
611  chillAST_node* _parent;
612  int _pos;
613 
614  inline ASTNodeClass* get() const {
615  return dynamic_cast<ASTNodeClass*>(_parent->getChild(_pos));
616  }
617 public:
618  chillAST_Child(chillAST_node* parent,int pos):_parent(parent),_pos(pos) {
619  while (parent->getNumChildren() <= pos)
620  parent->children.push_back(NULL);
621  // This will ensure that ASTNodeClass is a subclass of chillAST_node
622  parent->setChild(pos, NULL);
623  }
624 
625  chillAST_Child(const chillAST_Child<ASTNodeClass>&) = delete;
626  chillAST_Child(chillAST_Child<ASTNodeClass>&&) = delete;
627 
629  ASTNodeClass* operator=(ASTNodeClass *ptr) {
630  _parent->setChild(_pos, ptr);
631  return ptr;
632  }
633 
635  ASTNodeClass* operator=(const chillAST_Child<ASTNodeClass>& other) {
636  _parent->setChild(_pos, (ASTNodeClass*)other);
637  return (ASTNodeClass*)other;
638  }
639 
641  bool operator==(std::nullptr_t) { return !get(); }
642 
644  ASTNodeClass* operator ->() const { return get(); }
